  70:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****             (+) TxRxHalfCpltCallback  : SPI TxRx Half Completed callback
  71:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****             (+) ErrorCallback         : SPI Error callback
  72:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****             (+) AbortCpltCallback     : SPI Abort callback
  73:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_spi.c ****             (+) SuspendCallback       : SPI Suspend callback
